00:03:10.450 --> 00:03:14.370
One last bit: Noisy bursts were observed twice
in mouse development: once at the first cell

00:03:14.370 --> 00:03:18.420
fate decision when 32 cells decide to be an
embryo or support structures, and again 3

00:03:18.420 --> 00:03:19.900
days later as they specialize further.

00:03:19.900 --> 00:03:21.940
